HEADWORD: Selfsame
<hw>Self"same</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Self</ets>, a.
+ <ets>same</ets>.]</ety> <def>Precisely the same; the very same;
identical.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His servant was healed in the <qex>selfsame</qex> hour.</q>
<rj><qau>Matt. viii. 13.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-satisfaction</ent>⟦br⟧
